==English==

===Etymology===
{{enm}} [[blabben]], ''to talk foolishly'', [[back-formation]] from [[blaberen]].

===Verb===
'''blab''' ([[blabbed]], [[blabbing]])
#To tell tales; to [[gossip]] without reserve or discretion.

===Noun===
'''blab'''
#One who blabs; a babbler; a telltale; a [[gossip]] or [[gossiper]].

